":"公開見同自己行入去密室見，咁大分別都分唔到？邊個知佢哋傾過乜，出嚟又冇交代，賣生果入中聯辦做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20151109-taiwan-Xi-Jinping-and-Ma-Yingjeou-summit-full-text/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20151109-taiwan-Xi-Jinping-and-Ma-Yingjeou-summit-full-text%2F&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8hZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=c76b8cec\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20151109-taiwan-Xi-Jinping-and-Ma-Yingjeou-summit-full-text/</a><br />\n台灣兩岸事務主管部門──陸委會，7日公布總統馬英九在<strong>閉門會期</strong>間和中國國家主席習近平談話的全文。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你一樣唔知佢究竟講過乜野架,呢篇文係真定假架,小朋友"},{"pid":"e4a6dc85fdaf849b78e4c0dbff58678cb23406f5","tid":1075824,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"南韓瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6897eea2ebd26b39e2563e24fd28dae6edec7023","tid":1075824,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:26:40.000Z","msg":"熱狗呢？"},{"pid":"45d4c822382764df0b7d6e63e443e3b452dd1478","tid":1075824,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c99b89b94ac11cbfe466c7739dfa653a8fab312d","tid":1075824,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9e692561bc27bed27f5e91dbb92a84cc61f0173","tid":1075824,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0730cd3e0134f09652cbe87df2744e79b3479d2f","tid":1075824,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"睇吓兩岸條例再講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"條例第33-1條，臺灣地區人民、法人、團體或其他機構，非經各該主管機關許可，不得與大陸地區黨務、軍事、行政、具政治性機關 (構) 、團體或涉及對臺政治工作、影響國家安全或利益之機關 (構) 、團體為任何形式之合作行為。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"台灣馬英九見完